CKAN,Comprehensive,Knowledge,Archive,Network,is,an,open,source,data,portal,platform,that,provides,an,out,of,the,box,solution,for,managing,transferring,and,accessing,data,CKAN,operates,under,a,SaaS,model,and,was,created,to,help,data,publishers,make,their,data,open,and,available,The,CKAN,platform,contains,a,catalog,system,with,a,web,interface,data,visualization,and,analytics,workflow,support,access,control,data,storage,and,federated,structure,The,web,service,is,broken,down,into,two,distinct,parts,Search,and,Model,The,Search,API,exposes,methods,for,searching,resources,datasets,and,revisions,as,well,as,tag,counts,The,Model,API,provides,a,variety,of,GET,POST,and,PUT,operations,for,manipulating,creating,and,retrieving,model,resources,from,the,platform